Reo Hatate
REPORT
Joo Paulo is a goalkeeper known for his quick reflexes, smart decisions, and difficult
saves, especially under pressure. He stays focused and reacts fast when coming off his
line, whether to intercept crosses or close down attackers in 1v1 situations. His sharp
positioning and good timing help him deal with dangerous plays with confidence and
consistency.
With the ball at his feet, he is comfortable and prefers to make simple, safe passes to
keep possession. He avoids risky plays and usually chooses the smartest option available.

Featured Statistics Paulista 2024 and Serie A 2023
Joo Paulo has been a key player for Santos, standing out with
consistent performances and strong numbers.
In the 2024 Campeonato Paulista, he was the second goalkeeper
with the most saves, making 46 in total.
In the 2023 Brasileiro Srie A, he was also among the top
performers, finishing as the fourth goalkeeper with the most saves,
with 130 overall.
Another stats that shows his good form is xCG (expected goals
conceded), which measures how many goals a keeper is expected to
concede based on the quality of shots faced (Stats attached on the
last two pages of this PDF).
In 2023, his average xCG was 1.14, but he conceded only 1.08 goals
per game.
In 2024, he kept that level, with an xCG of 0.79 and only 0.73 goals
conceded.
This shows that Joo Paulo often saves difficult shots and performs
better than expected, making him a key part of the teams defense.

More information
Joo Paulo has been an important goalkeeper for Santos in recent years. He was the
teams starter until the middle of 2024, always showing a high level of performance
and reliability.
He has quick reactions, good positioning, and reads the game well, which helps in
1v1 situations and defensive duels. These qualities make him effective at stopping
dangerous plays and supporting the defense.
Known for his consistency, Joo Paulo stood out for making great saves, showing fast
reflexes and explosiveness in key moments across the seasons he played.
He also shows leadership and strong communication, helping organize the backline
and bringing confidence to the team. His calm presence and smart decision-making
make him a key figure on the field.
Conclusion
Joo Paulo is a reliable and experienced goalkeeper who has shown great consistency
over the seasons with Santos. He stands out for his quick reactions, strong shot-
stopping, and smart positioning. His leadership and communication bring confidence
to the defense. With good numbers and key saves, he has proven to be an important
player who performs well under pressure and helps the team in decisive moments.
